title: Father John Misty – “Generic Pop Song #3,” “Generic Pop Song #9,” & “Generic Pop Song #16″
text: Father John Misty co-wrote songs on Beyoncé and Lady Gaga's latest albums, and in interviews lately, he's been talking at great length about how calculated and grotesque the major-label pop world is. Now, he's taken to Soundcloud to share "Generic Pop Song #3," "Generic Pop Song #9," and "Generic Pop Song #16," three pop … More »
